Package: katherinemansfieldr
Title: A Package for Text Mining Katherine Mansfield's Short Stories
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Andrew", "Kim", email = "akim17@amherst.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
           person("Olivia", "Xu", email = "sxu17@amherst.edu",
                  role = c("aut")))
Description: This package contains machine45readable versions of the short stories from three of Katherine Mansfield's collections: The Garden Party, Bliss and Something Childish.This package also contains functions that parse text files and perform stylometric analysis tasks such asmeasuring lengths of sentences and words, measuring vocabulary richness, frequency of words and punctuation.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.0.0), dplyr
License: GNU General Public License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
